name: Wtbdc Protocol
description: World Trade Business Development Council (WTBDC) which is based in Turkey, operates as a business council. It aims to ensure the integration of trade between cntries with its activities all over the world. Our aim is to identify and manage trade and investment lunges both from Turkey to abroad, and abroad to Turkey. Increasing the share of Turkey in international trade activities in the world is among our biggest goals. WTP PROTOCOL the new dimension of international trade welcome to the future
